<td data-valign="TOP" width="45%"><p>(4.1251-1258) <span id="4.1251-1258"></span> "What land is this? Whither has the tempest hurled us? Would that, reckless of deadly fear, we had dared to rush on by that same path between the clashing rocks! Better were it to have overleapt the will of Zeus and perished in venturing some mighty deed. But now what should we do, held back by the winds to stay here, if ever so short a time? How desolate looms before us the edge of the limitless land!"</p></td>
<td data-valign="TOP" width="10%"></td>
